Dorsal cirri of median segments reniform, symmetrical, 
c.
twice as wide as long. Dorsal cirrophores asymmetrical, with narrow extensions on dorsal side of cirri (
Fig. 25F
). Neuropodium with supra-acicular lobes longer than subacicular lobes, with 
